# Design Source Files (Large & Proprietary)
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
*.sketch
*.fig
*.ai
*.psd
*.xd

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Archives
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
*.zip
*.rar
*.7z
*.tar.gz

